entries.femaleVariant: It's V. Took care of José.
Nice work. Really, really nice work.
The car's on its way.
Arasaka.
I'm still listening.
Did you learn who busted him out after he killed that badge?
Arasaka.
Nope.
Unfortunately, no.
But at least I learned something valuable about you.
A mistake. Could've been a big payday for us.
Wasn't the reason I was there.
entries.maleVariant: That wasn't the reason I was there.

entries.femaleVariant: No. It wasn't. See you, V.
Arasaka? You're telling me a megacorp was involved in the killing of some ordinary beat cop?
Joffrey's death was an accident. José was covered for another reason.
Padre, wait. They're loaded on Militech equipment.
How? They steal it?
You know more than you're telling.
I could stay - try to find out more.
Not sure, exactly, but... looks like they're plannin' something.
Such as?
Well... Dunno.
OK. See what I can find myself. Talk later.
Out with it.
There's a good chance that Arasaka's looking to pick a serious fight with Militech. Maybe even all-out war.
And? José's hit was meant to be their excuse? Kinda slim, don't ya think?
He and his crew were hired to launch a full-blown assault on an Arasaka facility, and do it using Militech equipment.
entries.maleVariant: He and his crew were hired to launch a full-blown assault on an Arasaka facility, and to do it using Militech equipment.

entries.femaleVariant: Attacking Arasaka... on Arasaka's behalf...? Shit... You need to get out of there.
But why war?
Why's Militech doing nothing?
But why war? They're still pickin' up pieces from the last one.
No bigger smokescreen than war. Maybe they need the attention off something else.
Not sure I even wanna know... You, Padre?
I'm just speculating here, but...
And Militech? Must've noticed Arasaka's moves.
entries.maleVariant: And Militech? They must've noticed Arasaka's moves.

entries.femaleVariant: Not this time, no. Not my board, not my game.
Likely. But Militech doesn't want war. They will delay, prepare, and prepare some more.
That info's worth a healthy heap in some circles.
See you 'round, V.
Yeah, be seein' ya.
Seein' as I'm already here, I could stick around – try to find out more.
Won't find nothing you don't already know. Location's already blown.
You know more than you're tellin'. Spill.
It's not just José. I've heard of other cases – same MO. This runs deep, V.
